---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Case Studies Dubai — Real ROI for SMEs | Aegis AI"
  description="Real AI results from Dubai businesses: 4× ROI, 3h saved/day, 74% of inquiries automated. Case studies across real estate, retail, and hospitality."
  canonicalPath="/results"
  ogImage="/assets/og-results.jpg"
>

<header class="hero-section">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <nav class="page-breadcrumb" style="justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1.5rem;" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span><strong>Results</strong>
    </nav>
    <div style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; background:rgba(0,227,253,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(0,227,253,0.28); border-radius:100px; padding:6px 16px; color:#004f58; font-size:0.875rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px;">bar_chart</span>
      Case Studies
    </div>
    <h1 style="max-width:720px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;">
      Real Results.<br><span class="gradient-text">Real Businesses. Real AI.</span>
    </h1>
    <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:1.125rem; max-width:620px; margin:1.5rem auto 0;">
      Every project we deliver is measured by one thing: the impact on your business. Here's what that looks like in practice.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- AGGREGATE METRICS -->
<section style="padding:4rem 0;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
    <div class="agg-bar">
      <div class="agg-grid" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1px 1fr 1px 1fr 1px 1fr; gap:0; align-items:center;">
        <div class="agg-stat">
          <p style="font-size:2.25rem; font-weight:800; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">3.2h</p>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.70); font-size:0.8125rem; margin:4px 0 0; line-height:1.5;">Avg. admin time saved per day</p>
        </div>
        <div class="agg-divider" style="height:60px;"></div>
        <div class="agg-stat">
          <p style="font-size:2.25rem; font-weight:800; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">4.1×</p>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.70); font-size:0.8125rem; margin:4px 0 0; line-height:1.5;">Average ROI within 12 months</p>
        </div>
        <div class="agg-divider" style="height:60px;"></div>
        <div class="agg-stat">
          <p style="font-size:2.25rem; font-weight:800; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">9 wks</p>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.70); font-size:0.8125rem; margin:4px 0 0; line-height:1.5;">Average implementation time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="agg-divider" style="height:60px;"></div>
        <div class="agg-stat">
          <p style="font-size:2.25rem; font-weight:800; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">100%</p>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.70); font-size:0.8125rem; margin:4px 0 0; line-height:1.5;">Clients who would recommend us</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CASE STUDIES -->
<section class="section" style="background:#e7eeff; padding-top:3rem;" aria-labelledby="cases-heading">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:900px;">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Case Studies</div>
      <h2 id="cases-heading">Projects That Delivered</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 1: Real Estate -->
    <div class="case-card">
      <div class="case-header">
        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:flex-start; gap:1rem; justify-content:space-between;">
          <div>
            <div class="industry-tag" style="margin-bottom:0.875rem;">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px;">home</span> Real Estate
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.25rem; color:#fff; max-width:540px; line-height:1.4; margin:0;">How a Dubai Property Agency Reduced Lead Response Time from 4 Hours to 4 Minutes</h3>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align:right; flex-shrink:0;">
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.60); font-size:0.75rem; margin:0;">Delivery time</p>
            <p style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.125rem; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">6 weeks</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">4 min</div><p class="result-label">Lead response time (was 4 hours)</p></div>
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">+40%</div><p class="result-label">Viewing bookings in 90 days</p></div>
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">3h/day</div><p class="result-label">Admin time saved per agent</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-col-grid" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:1.5rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
          <div><p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Challenge</p><p style="color:#42474e; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Agency receiving 200+ WhatsApp leads per day. Agents manually qualifying each one — average response time was 4 hours. High-intent leads were going cold and to competitors who responded faster.</p></div>
          <div><p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Solution</p><p style="color:#42474e; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">AI WhatsApp assistant that qualifies leads, answers property questions in Arabic and English, books viewing appointments, and auto-updates the CRM — 24/7 without human intervention on standard queries.</p></div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Timeline</p>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 1–2: Discovery, data mapping, CRM audit</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 3–4: AI training on property listings, FAQ database</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 5–6: Integration, testing, team training (1 day)</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 6: Go-live. Full adoption within 2 weeks.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 2: Retail -->
    <div class="case-card">
      <div class="case-header">
        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:flex-start; gap:1rem; justify-content:space-between;">
          <div>
            <div class="industry-tag" style="margin-bottom:0.875rem;">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px;">shopping_bag</span> Retail
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.25rem; color:#fff; max-width:540px; line-height:1.4; margin:0;">How a Dubai Retail Chain Cut Overstock by 28% With AI Demand Forecasting</h3>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align:right; flex-shrink:0;">
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.60); font-size:0.75rem; margin:0;">Delivery time</p>
            <p style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.125rem; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">8 weeks</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">−28%</div><p class="result-label">Overstock reduction</p></div>
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">−44%</div><p class="result-label">Stockout incidents</p></div>
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">+12%</div><p class="result-label">Gross margin improvement</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-col-grid" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:1.5rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
          <div><p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Challenge</p><p style="color:#42474e; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Multi-branch retailer with chronic overstock on slow-moving lines and stockouts on top sellers. Buying decisions relied on gut feel and spreadsheets. Each stockout meant lost revenue; each overstock tied up cash.</p></div>
          <div><p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Solution</p><p style="color:#42474e; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Demand forecasting AI trained on 3 years of sales data, seasonal patterns, and UAE-specific external signals — Ramadan, UAE National Day, Dubai Shopping Festival — plus weather and competitor promotions.</p></div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Timeline</p>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 1–3: Data extraction, cleaning, and model design</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 4–6: Model training and validation on historical data</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 7–8: Dashboard integration, buyer team training</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Results visible within first buying cycle.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 3: Hospitality -->
    <div class="case-card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="case-header">
        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:flex-start; gap:1rem; justify-content:space-between;">
          <div>
            <div class="industry-tag" style="margin-bottom:0.875rem;">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px;">hotel</span> Hospitality
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.25rem; color:#fff; max-width:540px; line-height:1.4; margin:0;">How a Dubai Hotel Group Automated 74% of Guest Inquiries With AI</h3>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align:right; flex-shrink:0;">
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.60); font-size:0.75rem; margin:0;">Delivery time</p>
            <p style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.125rem; color:#00e3fd; margin:0;">5 weeks</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">74%</div><p class="result-label">Standard inquiries handled automatically</p></div>
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">+0.4</div><p class="result-label">Guest satisfaction score improvement</p></div>
          <div class="result-pill"><div class="result-val">6h/day</div><p class="result-label">Staff time freed for high-value service</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-col-grid" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:1.5rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
          <div><p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Challenge</p><p style="color:#42474e; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Guest services team spending 6+ hours per day answering the same questions via WhatsApp and email — check-in times, pool access, restaurant hours, late checkout. Staff couldn't focus on high-touch guest experience.</p></div>
          <div><p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Solution</p><p style="color:#42474e; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">AI concierge handling all standard queries 24/7 in Arabic and English. Personalised to the hotel's brand voice. Complex requests and complaints escalated instantly to the duty manager with full conversation context.</p></div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Timeline</p>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 1–2: FAQ audit, WhatsApp API setup, brand voice mapping</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 3–4: AI training, escalation logic, staff briefing</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Week 5: Go-live. Satisfaction score up within 60 days.</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot-sm"></div><p style="color:#42474e;">Team reassigned to proactive guest experience roles.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INDUSTRIES COVERED -->
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="industries-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Expertise</div>
      <h2 id="industries-heading">Industries We've Delivered Results In</h2>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:20px; max-width:840px; margin:0 auto;">
      <a href="/industries/real-estate" class="industry-link-card">
        <div class="industry-link-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">home</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">Real Estate</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; line-height:1.5;">Lead scoring, WhatsApp AI, CRM automation</p>
        <p style="color:#006875; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; margin:0;">See solutions →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/industries/retail" class="industry-link-card">
        <div class="industry-link-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">shopping_bag</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">Retail &amp; E-commerce</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; line-height:1.5;">Demand forecasting, pricing, personalization</p>
        <p style="color:#006875; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; margin:0;">See solutions →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/industries/hospitality" class="industry-link-card">
        <div class="industry-link-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">hotel</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">Hospitality</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; line-height:1.5;">AI concierge, revenue management, scheduling</p>
        <p style="color:#006875; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; margin:0;">See solutions →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/industries/logistics" class="industry-link-card">
        <div class="industry-link-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">local_shipping</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; color:#00253b; font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">Logistics</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; line-height:1.5;">Route optimization, fleet AI, demand forecasting</p>
        <p style="color:#006875; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; margin:0;">See solutions →</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section" style="background:#e7eeff;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" style="text-align:center; max-width:680px; margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color:#fff; font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem); font-weight:800; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Your Business Could Be Next.</h2>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size:1.0625rem; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Book a free consultation. We'll identify the top 3 AI opportunities in your business — in 30 minutes.</p>
      <button onclick="openModal()" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.0625rem; padding:0.9375rem 2.5rem;">Book Free Consultation</button>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.40); font-size:0.8125rem; margin-top:1rem;">Free · No commitment · 100% Satisfaction Guarantee</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.case-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid rgba(0,37,59,0.08); border-radius:24px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,59,92,0.04); margin-bottom:2rem; }
    .case-header { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00253b,#006875); padding:2rem; }
    .case-body { padding:2rem; }
    .result-pill { background:rgba(0,104,117,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(0,104,117,0.12); border-radius:16px; padding:1rem 1.25rem; text-align:center; }
    .result-val { font-size:1.75rem; font-weight:800; color:#006875; }
    .result-label { color:#42474e; font-size:0.75rem; margin:4px 0 0; }
    .industry-tag { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:4px 12px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color:#fff; border-radius:100px; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; }
    .timeline-line { display:grid; grid-template-columns:8px 1fr; gap:0.75rem; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
    .timeline-dot-sm { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; background:#00e3fd; margin-top:6px; flex-shrink:0; }
    .agg-bar { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00253b 0%,#006875 100%); border-radius:24px; padding:3rem 2.5rem; }
    .agg-stat { text-align:center; }
    .agg-divider { width:1px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.20); }
    .industry-link-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid rgba(0,37,59,0.08); border-radius:20px; padding:1.75rem; text-align:center; box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,59,92,0.04); text-decoration:none; display:block; transition:transform .25s, box-shadow .25s; }
    .industry-link-card:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:0 24px 56px rgba(0,59,92,0.10); }
    .industry-link-icon { width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:14px; background:rgba(0,227,253,0.12); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin:0 auto 0.875rem; color:#006875; }
    @media(max-width:700px) { .agg-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr !important; } .case-col-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr !important; } }
</style>